results.occurrenceRemarks: These were fairly common in Bwabwata N.P., and we saw a number of them along the drive to our lunch spot and back. We were puzzled as to what they were for a while, because there is a fair amount of variation between young and old, males and females. Some we saw were very striped, some very spotted, and others more plain brown.
